metadata.name: bedroom, the most luxurious
metadata.description:
is filled with a bitter taste of traditional Chinese medicine.



A tall girl, dressed in traditional palace robes and a white veil, is intently reading the pulse of a young man lying on a bed, his face as white as paper.



"Congratulations TO GENERAL YE, THE TOXIN OF BROKEN INTESTINE DISPERSING ON YOUR BODY HAS BEEN SOLVED ALMOST, THE REST NEED TO TAKE MEDICINE AND REST WELL!"
